data.name: Label1.Text
data.value:
This command will create PDF, DWG and DXF files for all of the assembly component drawings.
Please make sure drawing files share the SAME NAME and FOLDER LOCATION as the assembly components in your local _vaultWIP folder. The best way to do this is to perform a "Get" on your assembly in Vault including attachments and library files.
Please check the file types you would like to batch print.
